=== WEAPON_BATTERY ===
# id: 88
# title: The Weapon Battery Remains
# chinese_title: 炮台残骸
# category: Wreckage
# mode: dungeon

The turret of a point-defense battery hangs at a broken angle, its barrel scarred and warped. The ammunition magazine below is partially intact, and targeting computer components could be salvaged. Scorch marks on the surrounding hull testify to the battle it fought.

* [Salvage ammunition components]
  ~ gain_item("emp_grenade")
  "弹" (dàn) — bullet, ammunition
* [Extract the targeting computer]
  ~ gain_radical("目")
  "准" (zhǔn) — to aim, accurate, precise
* [Recover weapon-grade alloys]
  ~ gain_gold(25)
  "钢" (gāng) — steel
* [Study the battle damage patterns]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "痕" (hén) — mark, trace, scar
